== logout in a non-login shell is refused:
shit: 1:1: error: Builtin 'logout': Cannot use 'logout' in a non-login shell.
     1 |  logout
       |  ^~~~~~ here.
shit: note: 'exit' may be used instead.
rc=1
== logout with a non-numeric operand is a located error:
shit: 1:1: error: Builtin 'logout': Cannot use 'logout' in a non-login shell.
     1 |  logout abc
       |  ^~~~~~~~~~ here.
shit: note: 'exit' may be used instead.
rc=1
